data.description: Welcome Home to the Hammocks of Cane Bay! This gorgeous ''Lincoln'' on this cul de sac that backs up to a pond has all the perks & then some. Master suite downstairs set in the back of the home with walk in his & hers closets  huge walk in tiled shower made for 2 will be the perfect retreat to end the day. But thats not the only place you will find your peace, out back in the private yard is your sunshine oasis in a 2022 installed heated salt water inground pool. 4th of July will never be the same for you - backed up to the YMCA your friends will be begging to come swim & enjoy the floor seats to the firework spectacular in the sky. Enjoy quiet mornings from the screened in patio or perched on the balcony taking it all in. There are so many spots here to have you swooning for this newaddress. 4 bedrooms upstairs with closets that could double as office space, all rooms with comfy upgraded carpeting opening up into the loft space where you can have home school area, gym or secondary living room with a view. Step outside onto the balcony overlooking the cul de sac - YES! This is YOUR HOME! 5 bedrooms, master downstairs, 3.5 bathrooms, quartz kitchen countertops, upgraded cabinets,gas stove, hardwood floors welcome you home daily - join the fun in Cane Bay, located close to YMCA, shop in Moncks Corner or Summerville, close to Nexton Parkway with easy access to major highways leading to Charleston & its glorious beaches. Let's go test the water in the pool today!
